column5: Bobby's Corner Closing For About A MonthBy CKDR News - September 27th, 2013 - 9:43amhttp://ckdr.net/news_clips/IMG_2108_1.jpgIf you are hoping to fill up in Vermilion Bay you will have to find somewhere else to go.The only gas station in Vermilion Bay is undergoing a major retrofit.Bobby's Corner will have to close down for about a month due to the renovations.
Unfortunately, his excellent selection of tackle is also unavailable.
I got enough tackle.but definately had to dig out my jerry cans.have to think ahead especially were we live.but ill survive.eagle river isnt that far away.they have tackle.gas.minnows.
